(OMC VENDOR CLEARANCE AND COMPLIANCE STANDARDS) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
50 740 Td
(1. Overview: Odisha Mining Corporation Vendor billing and verification standards version 3.0.) Tj
T*
(2. Invoice Registration: All invoices must be uploaded on the OMC ERP Portal within 7 days of service delivery.) Tj
T*
(3. Tax Compliance: Invoices must contain valid GSTIN numbers and matching HSN/SAC codes for iron ore logistics.) Tj
T*
(4. Payment Terms: Standard billing cycles clear payments within 30 days of successful verification by the Accounts Auditor.) Tj
T*
(5. Delay Penalty: A late interest fee of 1% monthly is applied if undisputed invoices are pending beyond 45 days.) Tj
T*
(6. Performance Bank Guarantees: Vendors must furnish an active PBG representing 5% of the total contract value.) Tj
T*
(7. Verification IDs: Contractors can check payment status using their designated Vendor ID \(e.g. VND-101, VND-102\).) Tj
T*
(8. Escalations: Unresolved payment clearance tickets can be escalated to the GM Finance at the Corporate Desk.) Tj
T*
ET

endstream
